The majority of the settled Bonebreaker land, the plateau is about  five miles by ten miles across, of relatively flat land.
Structures and jungle interweave here, with some sections of larger stone buildings jutting out here and There
Smoke rising from cooking fires, sounds of commerce and almost city life.
No obvious pattern at first but it is very well organized and maintained, the jungle beaten back only as far as necessary

~Shops~
* Meat, Fish, Furs and Skins
* Weapons, Armor
* Herbs, Supplies
* Guide companies, with proper resources
* Jewelery (decent)

Homes, Communities
Schools and "Guild Halls" for different groups in the society
Fighting pits
Gardens
